      "value": "<p>You release a shard of cryogenic energy at one creature within range. Make a ranged tech attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes [[/r 1d10]] kinetic damage. Hit or miss, the shard then explodes. The target and each creature within 5 feet of it must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take [[/r 2d6]] cold damage.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Overcharge Tech.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a tech slot of 2nd level or higher, the cold damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot level above 1st.</p>",
